title: There is no 'I do' for Drake, Serena Williams
text: There is no 'I do' for Drake, Serena Williams Friday, 9 October 2015 (1 minute ago) *Washington, Oct. 9 (ANI): If you were wishing to see Drake and Serena Williams happily married, then it's time to pop that bubble, as it is not happening anytime soon.* Washington, Oct. 9 (ANI): If you were wishing to see Drake and Serena Williams happily married, then it's time to pop that bubble, as it is not happening anytime soon. The 28-year-old rapper's representative has recently rejected all rumours that surfaced around the couple's engagement, reports TMZ.com. The rep said the rumours are completely untrue. (ANI) Serena Williams Calls Time on 2015 Season After Pulling Out of China Open 00:41 Serena Williams has called time on her 2015 season after withdrawing from the China Open and the WTA Finals in Singapore.
